summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1537, for the improvement of Interbay District of North Trunk Sewer District all in the City of Seattle, by construction of a main trunk sewer, under Ordinance No. 16615 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
